FBIS4-27527 "dreas106_c_94040" FBIS-EAS-94-106 Daily Report 29 May 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song Sends Message to President of Croatia Kim Il-song Sends Message to President of Croatia SK2905092494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0821 GMT 29 May 94 SK2905092494 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 29 (KCNA) -- President Kim Il-song of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea May 27 sent a message of greetings to Franjo Tudjman, president of the Republic of Croatia, on the national day of his country. The message wished him and the croatian people success in the work for peace and prosperity of Croatia.
